<font color=#70DB93>我去美国读书也是其中的原因之一</font>
and my going to America was just one of many things.

392
00:30:47,102 --> 00:30:49,058
<font color=#70DB93>他的祖籍是奥塞梯</font>
His side of the family is Ossetian,

393
00:30:49,186 --> 00:30:53,266
<font color=#70DB93>我们在政治上..有太多的冲突</font>
and we've had...more fights about politics

394
00:30:53,399 --> 00:30:54,941
<font color=#70DB93>多得我都记不清了</font>
than I care to remember.

395
00:30:55,067 --> 00:30:57,188
<font color=#70DB93>不 听着 我们要去伐利亚尼</font>
No, listen, we're trying to get to Variani,

396
00:30:57,619 --> 00:31:01,100
<font color=#70DB93>我想也许我们有幸可以搭你们的车</font>
and we wondered if we might be able to hitch a ride along with you guys.

397
00:31:01,363 --> 00:31:03,569
<font color=#70DB93>我们有好几年没说过话了</font>
We haven't spoken to each other in years.

398
00:31:05,842 --> 00:31:09,027
<font color=#70DB93>你的家人怎么样？他们肯定很担心你</font>
How about your family? They must be worried sick.

399
00:31:09,162 --> 00:31:11,269
<font color=#70DB93>不，不会，我没有家人</font>
No, no. I don't have one.

400
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:14,386
<font color=#70DB93>对不起</font>
Sorry.

401
00:31:14,917 --> 00:31:18,499
<font color=#70DB93>好了 终于和阿瓦利亚联系上了</font>
OK. Finally connected with Avaliani.

402
00:31:18,628 --> 00:31:21,712
<font color=#70DB93>他的车队会在拂晓时经过这里</font>
His convoy will pass here at first light,

403
00:31:21,939 --> 00:31:25,088
<font color=#70DB93>我们可以先搭他们的车 等离伐利亚尼1英里的时候</font>
and we can ride with them to about a mile from Variani.

404
00:31:25,216 --> 00:31:26,675
<font color=#70DB93>再下车自己想办法过去</font>
But then we're on our own.

405
00:31:26,801 --> 00:31:29,885
<font color=#70DB93>太好了 谢谢你 你们大家</font>
Great. Thank you. Both of you.

406
00:31:30,012 --> 00:31:32,301
<font color=#70DB93>嘿 伙计们！总统回来了！</font>
Hey, guys! The president's back on!

407
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:37,887
<font color=#70DB93>（我的公民们 各国领导们）</font>
'My fellow citizens and world leaders.

408
00:31:39,061 --> 00:31:41,730
<font color=#70DB93>（我们正在遭受俄罗斯军队的大规模进攻）</font>
'We are facing a massive attack by Russian forces

409
00:31:41,856 --> 00:31:43,311
<font color=#70DB93>他们现在控制了茨欣瓦利</font>
'who now control Tskhinvali.

410
00:31:44,441 --> 00:31:47,525
<font color=#70DB93>（我们不得不呼吁我们西方的所有朋友）</font>
'We have called out to all our friends in the West,

411
00:31:47,652 --> 00:31:50,586
<font color=#70DB93>（相信你们不会纵容这场侵略继续下去）</font>
'and trust that you will not allow this aggression to continue.

412
00:31:51,322 --> 00:31:55,106
<font color=#70DB93>（我已经命令我们的武装部队阻止任何军用车辆）</font>
'I have directed our Armed Forces to prevent all military vehicles

413
00:31:55,242 --> 00:31:57,824
<font color=#70DB93>（进入格鲁吉亚的国土）</font>
'from entering Georgian territory,

414
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:01,160
<font color=#70DB93>（并阻止任何对我们的攻击）</font>
'and to suppress any position attacking us.

415
00:32:02,456 --> 00:32:05,991
<font color=#70DB93>（我在此宣布全民动员令）</font>
'I hereby decree that a universal mobilisation

416
00:32:06,126 --> 00:32:07,620
<font color=#70DB93>（即刻生效）</font>
'is now in effect,

417
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:10,623
<font color=#70DB93>（所有预备役军官必须立即报到）</font>
'and all reserve officers must report in.

418
00:32:11,255 --> 00:32:14,042
<font color=#70DB93>（愿上帝保佑格鲁吉亚和我们所有的人）</font>
'May God save Georgia and all of us.'

419
00:32:32,941 --> 00:32:34,768
<font color=#70DB93>坐</font>
Sit down.

420
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:38,909
<font color=#70DB93>-你认为世界会听得到吗？ -但愿如此</font>
- Think the world heard me? - I hope so.

421
00:32:39,700 --> 00:32:42,190
<font color=#70DB93>但愿如此？</font>
You hope so?

422
00:32:42,323 --> 00:32:45,000
<font color=#70DB93>美国呢？助理国务卿布雷扎怎么说？</font>
The Americans? Bryza at the State Department?

423
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:50,151
<font color=#70DB93>布什总统已经非常明确地表示他们不会干涉 也不能</font>
Mr Bush has make it very clear that they will not intervene. Can't.

424
00:32:50,288 --> 00:32:51,913
<font color=#70DB93>至少在军事方面</font>
Not militarily, anyway.

425
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:53,530
<font color=#70DB93>那正是俄罗斯人希望的</font>
That's just what the Russians want.

426
00:32:54,266 --> 00:32:56,955
<font color=#70DB93>美国人肯定知道我别无选择</font>
The Americans must know that I had no choice.

427
00:32:57,086 --> 00:32:59,620
<font color=#70DB93>如果我无动于衷 俄罗斯人肯定早就闯进来了</font>
If I'd stood by, the Russians would be here by now,

428
00:33:00,046 --> 00:33:03,794
<font color=#70DB93>我们会失去整个国家！另一个车臣共和国！</font>
and my whole country would be lost! Another Chechenya!

429
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:07,209
<font color=#70DB93>如果美国人不帮忙 欧洲必须帮助我们！</font>
If the Americans won't help,then Europe must come to our aid!

430
00:33:07,344 --> 00:33:09,632
<font color=#70DB93>不管是谁 谁都可以</font>
But someone. Someone has to come.

431
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:12,586
<font color=#70DB93>事情变得棘手了 总统先生</font>
That's gonna be tough, Mr President.

432
00:33:13,015 --> 00:33:16,716
<font color=#70DB93>梅德韦杰夫称这是俄罗斯的“9.11”事件</font>
Medvedev is already playing this as a Russian 9/11.

433
00:33:16,852 --> 00:33:18,097
<font color=#70DB93>哦！拜托！哦！</font>
Oh, please! Oh!

434
00:33:18,229 --> 00:33:21,312
<font color=#70DB93>他在新闻发布会上指责你的士兵</font>
He's having press conferences accusing your soldiers

435
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:23,681
<font color=#70DB93>打死了茨欣瓦利的无辜平民</font>
of killing innocent civilians in Tskhinvali.

436
00:33:23,816 --> 00:33:26,521
<font color=#70DB93>-他管这个叫科索沃！ -真是令人发指！</font>
- He's calling this Kosovo! - But it's outrageous!

437
00:33:26,652 --> 00:33:30,269
<font color=#70DB93>我们尽了一切所能来减少平民伤亡</font>
We did everything we could to minimise civilian casualties

438
00:33:30,396 --> 00:33:31,624
<font color=#70DB93>但我们也要保卫自己！</font>
while defending ourselves!

439
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:37,199
<font color=#70DB93>这次我们争取别再把车弄坏了 好吗？</font>
Let's try and keep this car in one piece, eh?

440
00:33:37,328 --> 00:33:41,447
<font color=#70DB93>不然赫尔兹这辈子就不会再租给我任何东西了</font>
Otherwise Hertz will never rent me anything ever again.

441
00:33:49,546 --> 00:33:51,585
<font color=#70DB93>很高兴见到你 我的朋友</font>
It's good to see you, my friend.

442
00:33:51,714 --> 00:33:54,964
<font color=#70DB93>我也是 里佐 本以为重逢的光景能好些</font>
You, too, Rezo. I wish it were under better circumstances.

443
00:33:55,092 --> 00:33:57,464
<font color=#70DB93>-赛巴斯蒂安全都解释过了？ -是的</font>
- Sebastian explained everything? - Yes.

444
00:33:57,594 --> 00:33:59,670
<font color=#70DB93>-你介意我们拍摄吗？ -不</font>
- Do you mind if we film? - No.

445
00:34:01,222 --> 00:34:02,254
<font color=#70DB93>好了</font>
OK.

446
00:34:02,390 --> 00:34:04,881
<font color=#70DB93>上尉，这是塔蒂亚 她和家人失散了</font>
Captain, this is Tatia, whose family is missing.

447
00:34:05,017 --> 00:34:06,424
<font color=#70DB93>谢谢你们的护送</font>
Thanks for the escort.

448
00:34:07,562 --> 00:34:09,353
<font color=#70DB93>是的 我希望他们安全</font>
Yeah, I hope they are safe.

449
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:12,724
<font color=#70DB93>安德斯 你和我们一辆车</font>
Anders, you ride with us.

450
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:15,344
<font color=#70DB93>赛巴斯蒂安 你会在后面跟着</font>
Sebastian, you will follow.

451
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:17,603
<font color=#70DB93>那么 前线的情况如何？</font>
So, what's the situation at the front?

452
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:26,900
<font color=#70DB93>我们的情报显示来的不止是俄罗斯人</font>
Our intelligence indicates that not only the Russians are coming,

453
00:34:27,036 --> 00:34:29,609
<font color=#70DB93>还有志愿兵和雇佣军</font>
but volunteer militia and mercenaries

454
00:34:29,747 --> 00:34:32,913
<font color=#70DB93>来帮助俄军扫荡村庄</font>
to help the Russianscleanse the villages.

455
00:34:33,750 --> 00:34:38,495
<font color=#70DB93>如果你看到带白袖章和黑面具的人</font>
You see men with white armbands and black masks,

456
00:34:38,629 --> 00:34:40,835
<font color=#70DB93>千万别拍他们</font>
you don't take pictures.

457
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:44,332
<font color=#70DB93>也不要去躲 快跑</font>
You don't try to hide. You run.

458
00:34:44,467 --> 00:34:46,000
<font color=#70DB93>明白了吗？</font>
Understand?

459
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:56,008
<font color=#70DB93>你的朋友 安德斯 人很酷</font>
Your friend, Anders, is pretty cold.

460
00:34:56,144 --> 00:34:59,000
<font color=#70DB93>听着 他不是有意的</font>
Listen, he doesn't mean it.

461
00:34:59,313 --> 00:35:02,017
<font color=#70DB93>他和人交流有点困难</font>
He just has a hard time relating to people.

462
00:35:02,149 --> 00:35:05,482
<font color=#70DB93>你知道吗 他有过一些痛苦的经历 </font>
You know, he's been through some really bad shit.

463
00:35:05,610 --> 00:35:07,436
<font color=#70DB93>之前在伊拉克</font>
Iraq and before.

464
00:35:08,404 --> 00:35:09,661
<font color=#70DB93>但他是一个好人</font>
But he's a good guy.

465
00:35:10,489 --> 00:35:13,000
<font color=#70DB93>他很关心你还有你的家人</font>
He cares about you and your family.

466
00:35:14,576 --> 00:35:16,102
<font color=#70DB93>他只是想保证你的安全</font>
He just wants to keep you safe.

467
00:35:24,793 --> 00:35:27,959
<font color=#70DB93>-那是什么？ -意思是“天意”</font>
- What's that? - It means "God willing".

468
00:35:33,675 --> 00:35:36,000
<font color=#70DB93>对！说的不错！</font>
Yes! That's good!

469
00:35:36,636 --> 00:35:38,011
<font color=#70DB93>确实</font>
That's nice.

470
00:35:40,306 --> 00:35:45,000
<font color=#70DB93>你知道 里佐 真的很感谢你 但是</font>
You know, Rezo, thank you so much for this, but...

471
00:35:45,768 --> 00:35:48,200
<font color=#70DB93>我想我还是把这个还给你吧</font>
...I think I should give it back to you.

472
00:35:48,300 --> 00:35:51,435
<font color=#70DB93>不 我是特意给你的</font>
No. I give to you for reason.

473
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:56,475
<font color=#70DB93>你知道圣乔治的故事吗？</font>
Do you know the story of St George?

474
00:35:57,195 --> 00:35:59,317
<font color=#70DB93>嗯..士兵的守护神</font>
Uh... the patron saint of soldiers.

475
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:02,564
<font color=#70DB93>是的 他的模样遍布所有的教堂</font>
Yes. His image is in all churches.

476
00:36:03,200 --> 00:36:05,737
<font color=#70DB93>他曾是一个罗马士兵</font>
He was a Roman soldier

477
00:36:05,869 --> 00:36:10,000
<font color=#70DB93>由于拒绝放弃真相而被杀害</font>
martyred for refusing to abandon the truth.

478
00:36:10,172 --> 00:36:14,000
<font color=#70DB93>你们将伊拉克的真相公布于众</font>
You were trying to tell the truth in Iraq.

479
00:36:21,131 --> 00:36:26,000
<font color=#70DB93>我们只能送你们到这儿了 上帝与你们同在 我的朋友</font>
This is as far as we can take you.God be with you, my friend.

480
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:31,506
<font color=#70DB93>谢谢你</font>
Thank you.

481
00:37:19,389 --> 00:37:20,634
<font color=#70DB93>不知道？</font>
No?

482
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:25,000
<font color=#70DB93>这已经是第5个村子了 我们怎么才能找到他们？</font>
This is the fifth village.How are we supposed to find them?

483
00:37:28,605 --> 00:37:29,885
<font color=#70DB93>她说什么？</font>
What's she saying?

484
00:37:30,023 --> 00:37:32,500
<font color=#70DB93>她认为可以帮助我们 她要看看照片</font>
She thinks she can help us.She wants to see the pictures.

485
00:37:40,073 --> 00:37:42,279
<font color=#70DB93>她们说什么？他们说什么？</font>
What are they saying? What did they say?

486
00:37:42,408 --> 00:37:47,000
<font color=#70DB93>她说她表亲在艾奈维开了家小旅馆 离这儿5公里</font>
Her cousin owns an inn in Avnevi,5km from here,

487
00:37:47,200 --> 00:37:49,647
<font color=#70DB93>不久前有个新娘去了那里避难</font>
and he took in a bride seeking shelter.

488
00:37:50,081 --> 00:37:51,990
<font color=#70DB93>新娘和她父亲</font>
A bride and her father.

489
00:38:16,103 --> 00:38:17,812
<font color=#70DB93>我们来检查一下入住登记</font>
Let's check the registration.

490
00:38:25,352 --> 00:38:26,229
<font color=#70DB93>索芙！</font>
Sofi!

491
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:46,574
<font color=#70DB93>嘿</font>
Hey.

492
00:38:55,719 --> 00:38:56,546
<font color=#70DB93>嘿</font>
Hey.

493
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:08,182
<font color=#70DB93>-他在说什么？ -战斗机！战斗机！</font>
- What's he saying? - Jets! Jets!

494
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:50,000
<font color=#70DB93>各位 快找个地方躲起来 现在！</font>
Guys, we need to get to a shelter. Now!

495
00:40:00,732 --> 00:40:02,476
<font color=#70DB93>我们这下面没准备多少吃的</font>
We do not have much down here,

496
00:40:02,609 --> 00:40:05,566
<font color=#70DB93>不过你们尽管吃吧</font>
but you are welcome to have it.

497
00:40:06,069 --> 00:40:06,942
<font color=#70DB93>你们一定饿了</font>
You must be hungry.

498
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:27,209
<font color=#70DB93>俄军坦克已闯入格鲁吉亚的非争议地区</font>
Russian tanks are crossing into undisputed Georgian territory.

499
00:40:28,422 --> 00:40:31,292
<font color=#70DB93>全国范围内的机场都遭到了空袭</font>
The air force is bombing airfields all across the country.

500
00:40:33,344 --> 00:40:35,878
<font color=#70DB93>有战舰封锁了我们的港口</font>
Battleships are moving in to block our ports.

501
00:40:37,013 --> 00:40:39,718
<font color=#70DB93>-我的上帝 -我们今天早上出发的时候</font>
- My God. - We leave at first light.

502
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:43,299
<font color=#70DB93>阿瓦利亚尼告诉我除了俄军还有志愿兵</font>
Avaliani told me volunteer militia are coming with the Russians.

503
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:46,303
<font color=#70DB93>我们应该先休息一下</font>
We should try to get some rest.

504
00:42:35,254 --> 00:42:39,200
<font color=#70DB93>赛巴斯蒂安?赛巴斯蒂安,醒醒!快!我们得走了!来吧!</font>
Sebastian? Sebastian, wake up! Quickly! We've gotta go! Come on!

505
00:42:53,553 --> 00:42:55,821
<font color=#70DB93>不行了,有直升机.塔蒂亚,找地方躲起来!</font>
We can't. There's choppers.Tatia, hiding places!

506
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:00,625
<font color=#70DB93>这边有座桥!</font>
Bridge over this way!

507
00:43:17,189 --> 00:43:19,941
<font color=#70DB93>-我们得走另一条路! -我们要拍下这个</font>
- We have to go another way! - We have to see this.

508
00:43:20,067 --> 00:43:22,557
<font color=#70DB93>过来.这边.过河.过来</font>
Come on. This way. The river. Come on.

509
00:43:48,249 --> 00:43:50,587
<font color=#70DB93>无论发生什么都不要出声!</font>
Not a sound! No matter what happens.

510
00:44:02,185 --> 00:44:03,466
<font color=#70DB93>他在说什么?</font>
What did he say?

511
00:44:03,700 --> 00:44:06,520
<font color=#70DB93>他说他要见警长和市长</font>
He said he wants the chief of police and the mayor.

512
00:44:27,589 --> 00:44:30,000
<font color=#70DB93>不！我们应该做点什么！</font>
No! We have to do something!

513
00:44:30,200 --> 00:44:32,202
<font color=#70DB93>在这儿我们什么都做不了</font>
There's nothing we can do.

514
00:44:32,335 --> 00:44:34,441
<font color=#70DB93>他们会把我们全都杀了的!</font>
They'll kill us all!

515
00:45:16,022 --> 00:45:17,233
<font color=#70DB93>天啊!</font>
Jesus!

516
00:45:39,183 --> 00:45:42,200
<font color=#70DB93>我们快她妈离开这儿吧,赛巴斯蒂安</font>
Let's get the fuck out of here, Sebastian.

517
00:45:42,269 --> 00:45:44,359
<font color=#70DB93>再等一下</font>
Just one sec.

518
00:45:47,600 --> 00:45:49,000
<font color=#70DB93>把他们都干掉!</font>
Clear them out!

519
00:45:51,152 --> 00:45:53,476
<font color=#70DB93>该死！我们走！-我们走！走！</font>
- Shit! Let's go!- Let's go! Go!

519
00:45:58,000 --> 00:46:00,000
<font color=#70DB93>(米-24"雌鹿"武装直升机)</font>

520
00:46:49,550 --> 00:46:51,700
<font color=#70DB93>我的上帝！怎么会这样!</font>
My God! This can't be happening!

521
00:46:53,700 --> 00:46:56,000
<font color=#70DB93>嘘!安静!安静!</font>
Shh! Stay calm! Stay calm!

522
00:48:36,000 --> 00:48:37,650
<font color=#70DB93>所有人,都进来,塔蒂亚,让大家都躲起来</font>
Everybody, in here. Tatia, hide everybody.

523
00:48:37,650 --> 00:48:41,000
<font color=#70DB93>好!我们会找到出去的路!过来！快快！</font>
-OK! - We'll find a way out! Come on! Quick! Quick!

524
00:49:12,295 --> 00:49:13,526
<font color=#70DB93>嘘!嘘!</font>
Shh, shh!

525
00:49:40,219 --> 00:49:42,000
