589
00:55:11,100 --> 00:55:14,000
<font color=#70DB93>那个人打你的时候掉在地上了</font>
It's in the ground where you fell after that guy hit you.

590
00:55:14,100 --> 00:55:16,262
<font color=#70DB93>我过去扶你的时候顺手把它埋起来了</font>
