<font color=#70DB93>用英语说</font>
In English.

603
00:57:01,512 --> 00:57:03,020
<font color=#70DB93>你确定他们没有伤害你吗？</font>
Are you sure they didn't hurt you?

604
00:57:03,155 --> 00:57:06,100
<font color=#70DB93>是,是啊</font>
Yes, yes.

605
00:57:06,200 --> 00:57:09,566
<font color=#70DB93>那么他们对你做了什么了 你去了那么长时间</font>
So, what did they do to you? You were gone a long time.

606
00:57:11,912 --> 00:57:14,079
<font color=#70DB93>你什么都没有告诉他们吗？</font>
You didn't tell them anything, did you?

607
00:57:14,207 --> 00:57:18,000
<font color=#70DB93>哦,天啊！</font>
Oh, Christ!

608
00:57:19,010 --> 00:57:24,037
<font color=#70DB93>这棋盘式我儿子送给我的礼物 萨沙 他在阿富汗阵亡了</font>
