609
00:57:48,552 --> 00:57:52,518
<font color=#70DB93>不错啊 安德斯先生 不错</font>
Not bad, Mr Anders. Not bad.

610
00:57:55,282 --> 00:57:58,267
<font color=#70DB93>我的死时只有21岁</font>
My Sasha was only 21 when he was killed.

611
00:58:00,000 --> 00:58:02,318
<font color=#70DB93>他被敌军士兵捉住了</font>
He was captured by enemy soldiers.

612
00:58:02,454 --> 00:58:05,573
<font color=#70DB93>你能想象得到他们对他做了什么</font>
You can imagine the things they did to him.

613
00:58:05,708 --> 00:58:08,258
<font color=#70DB93>这并不能成为你在这里胡作非为的借口</font>
That doesn't excuse what you did here.

614
00:58:09,502 --> 00:58:11,874
<font color=#70DB93>当然不能</font>
Of course it doesn't.

615
00:58:12,005 --> 00:58:16,167
<font color=#70DB93>我只是这样说..你知道我是明白的</font>
I just say so...you know I understand.

616
00:58:16,299 --> 00:58:18,755
<font color=#70DB93>明白什么？</font>
Understand what?

617
00:58:18,885 --> 00:58:21,044
<font color=#70DB93>你的眼神</font>
That look in your eyes.

618
00:58:21,179 --> 00:58:23,799
<font color=#70DB93>失去家人之后的那种空洞</font>
The emptiness that comes from burying your family.

619
00:58:53,815 --> 00:58:58,000
<font color=#70DB93>你失去了你的父母 交通事故 是吗？</font>
You lost your parents. Car accident, wasn't it?

