00:59:06,800 --> 00:59:12,256
<font color=#70DB93>家人死后我们都开始追寻战争</font>
That we both asked for combat after family death.

623
00:59:14,607 --> 00:59:16,514
<font color=#70DB93>如果有人问我们</font>
And if people asked us,

624
00:59:17,351 --> 00:59:22,495
<font color=#70DB93>我确定我们能给出很多我们这样做的原因</font>
I'm sure we'd give them many reasons for why we did it.

625
00:59:24,000 --> 00:59:25,850
<font color=#70DB93>但如果我们直言不讳</font>
But if we are honest...

626
00:59:30,737 --> 00:59:36,524
<font color=#70DB93>我认为我们只是在追寻声音</font>
...I think we just sought noise,

627
00:59:37,600 --> 00:59:40,325
<font color=#70DB93>来淹没其他的思想</font>
to drown out all other thoughts.

628
00:59:41,746 --> 00:59:43,569
<font color=#70DB93>去忘记</font>
To forget.

629
00:59:44,000 --> 00:59:48,126
<font color=#70DB93>片刻之后 在那声音中</font>
Then after a while, in that noise,

630
00:59:48,252 --> 00:59:51,750
<font color=#70DB93>你开始感到自己免疫了</font>
you start to feel... immune.

631
00:59:53,281 --> 00:59:56,132
<font color=#70DB93>我是正确的吗？</font>
Am I right?

632
