01:01:59,262 --> 01:02:02,031
<font color=#70DB93>我可以开始了吗,少校？</font>
May I begin, Colonel?

663
01:02:02,156 --> 01:02:03,816
<font color=#70DB93>等一下</font>
Hold on.

664
01:02:07,019 --> 01:02:10,000
<font color=#70DB93>我们现在必须为自己考虑了</font>
We must think of ourselves now.

665
01:02:10,100 --> 01:02:11,952
<font color=#70DB93>而不是两个陌生人！</font>
Not two strangers!

666
01:02:12,700 --> 01:02:16,885
<font color=#70DB93>你认为他们不会离开我们？他们会像这个世界一样抛弃我们</font>
You think they wouldn't leave us? They will abandon us like the world has!

667
01:02:18,377 --> 01:02:21,413
<font color=#70DB93>塔蒂亚,告诉我录像在哪儿？</font>
Tatia, tell me where the recording is?

668
01:02:21,689 --> 01:02:23,579
<font color=#70DB93>你们美国人！</font>
You Americans!

669
01:02:23,716 --> 01:02:27,467
<font color=#70DB93>萨卡什维利发动了这场战争！</font>
Saakashvili started this war!

670
01:02:27,600 --> 01:02:29,980
<font color=#70DB93>你明白吗？</font>
You understand?

671
01:02:30,000 --> 01:02:34,000
<font color=#70DB93>我们在这儿只是为了保护我们在南奥塞梯的人！</font>
We are here just to protect our people in South Ossetia!

672
01:02:34,001 --> 01:02:36,224
<font color=#70DB93>我他妈才不管你想要保护谁！</font>
I can't give a fuck who you think you're trying to protect!

673
01:02:36,352 --> 01:02:42,476
<font color=#70DB93>但是我想知道是什么让你去射杀一个妇女的</font>
But I would love to know how shooting an old woman helps you to do it.

674
01:02:44,649 --> 01:02:48,599
<font color=#70DB93>我只是一名士兵,我有我的使命</font>
I'm only a soldier.I have my orders.

675
01:02:48,736 --> 01:02:51,820
<font color=#70DB93>格鲁吉亚已经输掉了这场战争</font>
Georgia already lost this war.

676
01:03:19,054 --> 01:03:21,722
<font color=#70DB93>-你不听我的 -你怎么..？</font>
- You didn't listen to me.- How the hell did you...?

677
01:03:21,847 --> 01:03:25,013
<font color=#70DB93>我们正在撤退.随后听说这里被袭击了</font>
We had to fall back.Then we heard the attack here.

678
01:03:25,142 --> 01:03:27,549
<font color=#70DB93>-他们抓住了赛巴斯蒂安 -好的 我们会解决</font>
- They got Sebastian.- Yes. We are on it.

679
01:03:27,686 --> 01:03:30,272
<font color=#70DB93>他们抓住了塔蒂亚和她的家人</font>
And they got Tatia and her family.

680
01:03:30,505 --> 01:03:33,309
<font color=#70DB93>-哪条路？ -在地下室的牢房</font>
- Which way? - The jail in the basement.

681
01:04:12,000 --> 01:04:13,552
<font color=#70DB93>-你还好吗,伙计? -是的</font>
- Are you all right, bucko? - Yeah.

682
01:04:13,683 --> 01:04:14,714
<font color=#70DB93>还好？</font>
Yeah?

683
01:04:19,000 --> 01:04:21,200
<font color=#70DB93>我们可用他们做盾牌！</font>
We can use them as shields!

684
01:04:25,301 --> 01:04:27,000
<font color=#70DB93>钥匙！</font>
Keys!

685
01:04:31,000 --> 01:04:32,000
<font color=#70DB93>你回来了！</font>
You came back!

686
01:04:32,115 --> 01:04:33,490
<font color=#70DB93>-是啊 你受伤了吗？ -没有</font>
- Yeah. You hurt? - No.

687
01:04:33,616 --> 01:04:35,200
<font color=#70DB93>好的 我们走</font>
OK. Let's go.

688
01:04:35,300 --> 01:04:36,000
<font color=#70DB93>塔蒂亚！</font>
Tatia!

689
01:04:36,135 --> 01:04:39,526
<font color=#70DB93>不,我不能相信你</font>
No, I can't trust you.

690
01:04:39,663 --> 01:04:42,663
<font color=#70DB93>塔蒂亚，我是你爸爸...</font>
Tatia, I'm your father...

691
01:04:42,791 --> 01:04:45,364
<font color=#70DB93>他们需要我的帮助</font>
They need my help.

692
01:04:48,553 --> 01:04:52,000
<font color=#70DB93>不,你和你的朋友在一起更安全</font>
No. You'll be safer with your friends.

693
01:04:57,261 --> 01:04:58,719
<font color=#70DB93>医生！</font>
Medic!

694
01:05:00,130 --> 01:05:04,013
<font color=#70DB93>-你还好吗？-没事..只是我的胳膊</font>
- Are you okay? - It's nothing... just my arm.

695
01:05:04,142 --> 01:05:05,850
<font color=#70DB93>我说医生！</font>
Medic I said!

696
01:05:05,977 --> 01:05:08,930
<font color=#70DB93>抓住他们！</font>
Get them!

697
01:05:18,012 --> 01:05:19,306
<font color=#70DB93>你紧跟着我</font>
You stay close to me.

698
01:05:39,505 --> 01:05:41,580
<font color=#70DB93>发动车辆！</font>
Get the vehicles started!

699
01:06:07,103 --> 01:06:09,359
<font color=#70DB93>我们得找到存储卡</font>
We need to get the memory card!

700
01:06:10,164 --> 01:06:11,608
<font color=#70DB93>我知道！</font>
I know!

701
01:06:18,546 --> 01:06:19,891
<font color=#70DB93>掩护我们！</font>
Cover us!

702
01:06:21,040 --> 01:06:22,499
<font color=#70DB93>过来！进去！</font>
Come on! Get in!

703
01:06:23,583 --> 01:06:26,143
<font color=#70DB93>进去！快！</font>
Get in! Quickly!

704
01:06:39,179 --> 01:06:40,922
<font color=#70DB93>坦克来了 上尉！</font>
Tank coming, Captain!

705
01:06:42,057 --> 01:06:44,000
<font color=#70DB93>-上尉！-我知道！</font>
- Captain!- I know!

706
01:07:37,695 --> 01:07:39,687
<font color=#70DB93>低下头！</font>
Stay down!

707
01:07:47,000 --> 01:07:50,736
<font color=#70DB93>我得下去！我们有战争罪的证据！</font>
I have to get out! We have evidence of a war crime!

708
01:07:50,800 --> 01:07:53,000
<font color=#70DB93>在果园周围的那条路上见！</font>
Meet you where the road comes around the orchard!

709
01:08:01,641 --> 01:08:03,248
<font color=#70DB93>真是个疯子</font>
That guy's crazy.

709
01:09:01,000 --> 01:09:03,000
<font color=#70DB93>（LAW单兵火箭筒）</font>

710
01:09:15,000 --> 01:09:17,000
<font color=#70DB93>减速！慢点！</font>
Slow down! Slow down!

711
01:09:18,000 --> 01:09:19,178
<font color=#70DB93>来吧！来吧！</font>
Come on! Come on!

712
01:09:19,314 --> 01:09:21,057
<font color=#70DB93>你拿到存储卡了吗？ -是的</font>
- Did you get the memory card? - Yeah.

713
01:09:23,176 --> 01:09:26,000
<font color=#70DB93>-你还好吗？-是的，我很好</font>
- Are you all right? - Yeah, I'm fine.

714
01:09:26,500 --> 01:09:28,513
<font color=#70DB93>我们快出去了</font>
We're almost out.

715
01:09:36,453 --> 01:09:37,912
<font color=#70DB93>爸爸！</font>
Papa!

716
01:09:38,038 --> 01:09:39,201
<font color=#70DB93>趴下！</font>
Get down!

717
01:11:11,700 --> 01:11:17,323
<font color=#70DB93>梅德韦杰夫拒绝了新的和平提议</font>
Medvedev has refused new peace proposals.

718
01:11:17,455 --> 01:11:19,328
<font color=#70DB93>哪部分？</font>
Which parts?

719
01:11:19,457 --> 01:11:20,951
<font color=#70DB93>所有的</font>
All of them.

720
01:11:21,083 --> 01:11:24,830
<font color=#70DB93>他告诉萨科奇说他们有自己的需要</font>
He told Sarkozy that they have their own demands.

721
01:11:24,962 --> 01:11:29,088
<font color=#70DB93>-什么需要？ -他们明天要把他们送出去</font>
- What possible demands? - They're sending them over tomorrow.

722
01:11:29,214 --> 01:11:33,259
<font color=#70DB93>我要宣布单方面停火</font>
I am reinstating unilateral ceasefire.

723
01:11:33,385 --> 01:11:36,504
<font color=#70DB93>-总统先生...-我们所有的军队 停火</font>
- Mr President... - All our troops, ceasefire.

724
01:11:37,800 --> 01:11:41,000
<font color=#70DB93>撤退到第比利斯.我们必须保卫我们的首都</font>
Fall back to Tbilisi.We must defend our capital.

725
01:11:41,100 --> 01:11:46,000
<font color=#70DB93>如果外界对我们的姿态没有任何回应,这就是自杀！</font>
If the world does not respond to this gesture, it is suicide!

726
01:11:46,000 --> 01:11:48,000
<font color=#70DB93>这是我们幸存的唯一选择</font>
It is the only chance we have for survival.

727
01:12:01,075 --> 01:12:03,779
<font color=#70DB93>我们应该在中午之前到达哥里</font>
We should reach Gori by noon.

728
01:12:04,000 --> 01:12:06,365
<font color=#70DB93>它是最近的有广播中心的城市</font>
It is the nearest city with broadcast centre.

729
01:12:07,455 --> 01:12:11,100
<font color=#70DB93>那里还有更快的路线吗？我们现在得把录像播出去</font>
Isn't there a faster route? We need to get this footage out now.

730
01:12:12,201 --> 01:12:15,122
<font color=#70DB93>没有 我们必须离开公路</font>
No. We must stay off road.

731
01:13:12,310 --> 01:13:16,341
<font color=#70DB93>我对你失去的表示抱歉</font>
I'm... sorry for your loss.

732
01:13:19,432 --> 01:13:22,100
<font color=#70DB93>我不是冒犯.这..</font>
I don't mean to offend. It's...

733
01:13:23,144 --> 01:13:28,000
<font color=#70DB93>只是在我的生命中已经失去了太多的人</font>
It's just I've lost many people in my life.

734
01:13:30,275 --> 01:13:36,443
<font color=#70DB93>但是我相信我们面对的所有磨难..</font>
But I believe that all the trials that we face...

735
01:13:37,598 --> 01:13:41,000
<font color=#70DB93>都是在指引我们达到目的</font>
...lead us to our purpose.

736
01:13:44,245 --> 01:13:46,000
<font color=#70DB93>谢谢你</font>
Thank you.

737
01:13:54,000 --> 01:13:56,000
<font color=#70DB93>你相信什么 安德斯？</font>
What do you believe, Anders?

738
01:14:04,470 --> 01:14:06,012
<font color=#70DB93>我不知道</font>
I don't know.

739
01:15:06,605 --> 01:15:09,000
<font color=#70DB93>你们放弃了自己的岗位？</font>
You're abandoning your post?

740
01:15:09,108 --> 01:15:11,100
<font color=#70DB93>是总统的命令</font>
By order of the President.

741
01:15:11,234 --> 01:15:13,226
<font color=#70DB93>撤回所有军队</font>
All troops are to fall back

742
01:15:13,362 --> 01:15:17,000
<font color=#70DB93>保卫第比利斯</font>
and report to defend Tbilisi.

743
01:15:18,000 --> 01:15:19,441
<font color=#70DB93>哥里市要沦陷了</font>
Gori is going to fall.

744
01:15:19,575 --> 01:15:23,275
<font color=#70DB93>我很抱歉.我有我的命令</font>
I'm sorry. I have my orders.

745
01:15:23,411 --> 01:15:25,284
<font color=#70DB93>他在说什么？</font>
What did he say?

746
01:15:25,413 --> 01:15:29,161
<font color=#70DB93>-他们要抛弃城市 -我们正要去那儿！</font>
- They're abandoning the city. - We've got to get in there!

747
01:15:29,291 --> 01:15:32,000
<font color=#70DB93>-你打算怎么办？ -我不会逃走</font>
- What do you wanna do? - I will not run.

748
01:15:33,169 --> 01:15:34,877
<font color=#70DB93>我不会抛下我的祖国！</font>
I will not lose my country!

749
01:15:35,005 --> 01:15:38,005
<font color=#70DB93>为了格鲁吉亚的自由我战斗的太多了</font>
I've fought in too many wars to keep Georgia free.

750
01:16:47,000 --> 01:16:50,437
<font color=#70DB93>-哪条路是去广播中心的？-那条！东边！</font>
- Which way to the broadcast centre? - That way! East!

751
01:17:07,000 --> 01:17:10,000
<font color=#70DB93>我很抱歉 我们必须把你们留在这儿了</font>
I'm sorry. We must leave you here.

752
01:17:10,050 --> 01:17:14,000
<font color=#70DB93>我得尝试建立防御 你们必须尽最大努力离开城市</font>
I need to attempt a defence. As soon as you can, you must leave the city.

753
01:17:14,001 --> 01:17:16,955
<font color=#70DB93>这里会变得非常危险</font>
It will become very dangerous.

754
01:17:17,090 --> 01:17:19,091
<font color=#70DB93>-多保重,里佐 -上帝与你同在-</font>
- Take care, Rezo. - God be with you.

755
01:17:26,306 --> 01:17:28,180
<font color=#70DB93>-你拿着存储卡呢吗？ -是的</font>
- You got the card? - Yeah.

756
01:17:28,308 --> 01:17:30,383
<font color=#70DB93>首先,我们需要找一个愿意播放录像的网络</font>
First, we need an upload code

757
01:17:30,390 --> 01:17:33,000
<font color=#70DB93>并得到它的上传代码</font>
from a network willing to accept the footage.

758
01:17:34,480 --> 01:17:37,266
<font color=#70DB93>该死！他们都走了！</font>
Shit! They've gone!

759
01:17:43,737 --> 01:17:47,437
<font color=#70DB93>-我们现在该做些什么？ -我们需要一部电话</font>
- What do we do now? - We need a phone.

760
01:17:53,500 --> 01:17:56,913
<font color=#70DB93>-（国际接线员）-接一个通美国的付费电话</font>
- 'International operator.' - A collect call to the USA.

761
01:17:57,040 --> 01:17:59,000
<font color=#70DB93>我得吃点东西</font>
I need to eat something.

762
01:18:00,000 --> 01:18:02,752
<font color=#70DB93>嘿！我找到水了！</font>
Hey! I got water!

763
01:18:02,878 --> 01:18:05,000
<font color=#70DB93>-嘿,卡琳  -感谢上帝！</font>
- Hey, Karin. - 'Thank God!'

764
01:18:05,100--> 01:18:07,755
<font color=#70DB93>-你们还好吗？ -是的 我们在哥里</font>
- You guys all right? - 'Yeah. We're in Gori.'

765
01:18:08,000 --> 01:18:10,000
<font color=#70DB93>哥里？那里被轰炸了！</font>
Gori? It's been bombed!

766
01:18:10,093 --> 01:18:12,250
<font color=#70DB93>-我知道 -你得离开</font>
- I know. - 'You need to get out.'

767
01:18:12,387 --> 01:18:13,417
<font color=#70DB93>找到硬币了！</font>
Got coins!

768
01:18:13,554 --> 01:18:16,756
<font color=#70DB93>不 我们有一些东西需要上传,我需要一个网络！</font>
No. We have something we need to upload. I need a network!

769
01:18:16,890 --> 01:18:20,000
<font color=#70DB93>-俄军可能会攻占.. -卡琳,我知道!听我说！</font>
- The Russians are likely to take... - 'Karin, I know! Listen to me!'

770
01:18:20,102 --> 01:18:22,887
<font color=#70DB93>我们亲眼目睹了一些事.杀戮.在一个村庄的处决</font>
We witnessed something. Killings. Executions in a village.

771
01:18:23,020 --> 01:18:25,345
<font color=#70DB93>赛巴斯蒂安全都录下来了.我们得把它播出来.</font>
Sebastian got it all on tape. We have to get it out.

772
01:18:25,481 --> 01:18:28,150
<font color=#70DB93>-（现在） -是的,但是怎么办？</font>
- 'Now.' - Yeah, but how?

773
01:18:28,275 --> 01:18:33,000
<font color=#70DB93>这里的媒体中心支持卫星上传</font>
There's a media centre building here with a satellite upload capability.

774
01:18:33,029 --> 01:18:36,444
<font color=#70DB93>我们能进去,但我们需要一个愿意</font>
We can get in,but we need for a network

775
01:18:36,573 --> 01:18:40,000
<font color=#70DB93>帮我们播放的网络..一个接入码</font>
to accept the feed and give us... an access code.

776
01:18:40,010 --> 01:18:43,000
<font color=#70DB93>她最好快点!空袭就要来了</font>
She'd better hurry! The bombing's winding down.

777
01:18:43,100 --> 01:18:45,622
<font color=#70DB93>也就是地面部队已经做好准备了</font>
Which means the ground troops are getting ready.

778
01:18:45,700 --> 01:18:48,000
<font color=#70DB93>-你听到了吗？ -是的,但是安德斯..</font>
- You hear that? - 'Yeah, but Anders...'

779
01:18:48,050 --> 01:18:51,366
<font color=#70DB93>我已经跟大家说了.没有人在乎</font>
I have already tried everyone.No one cares.

780
01:18:51,503 --> 01:18:56,170
<font color=#70DB93>（但我会再试试罗杰.麦提尔尼.如果有人能办到,就是他了）</font>
'But I'll try Roger McTierney.If anyone can get it on, it's him.'

781
01:18:56,173 --> 01:18:58,000
<font color=#70DB93>好,好,好的</font>
Yeah, yeah. OK.

782
01:19:00,635 --> 01:19:01,094
<font color=#70DB93>给</font>
Here.

783
01:19:03,680 --> 01:19:05,950
<font color=#70DB93>给我那些硬币,我们找夏达奇曼</font>
Give me those coins.Let's try the Dutchman.

784
01:19:06,098 --> 01:19:07,212
<font color=#70DB93>好的</font>
Yeah.

785
01:19:28,325 --> 01:19:29,570
<font color=#70DB93>友军！</font>
Friendlies!

786
01:19:31,000 --> 01:19:33,070
<font color=#70DB93>别开枪！</font>
Hold your fire!

787
01:19:41,002 --> 01:19:42,994
<font color=#70DB93>你看到地面部队了吗？</font>
Have you seen ground troops?

788
01:19:43,129 --> 01:19:45,122
<font color=#70DB93>听到了吗？</font>
Hear that?

789
01:19:49,000 --> 01:19:50,200
<font color=#70DB93>空袭停止了</font>
The bombing's stopped.

790
01:19:52,000 --> 01:19:54,000
<font color=#70DB93>守住阵地！</font>
Defensive positions!

791
01:19:54,100 --> 01:19:55,430
<font color=#70DB93>行动！</font>
Move out!

792
01:19:58,000 --> 01:20:00,000
<font color=#70DB93>-卡琳？ -（他不干）</font>
- Karin? - 'He won't do it.'

793
01:20:00,160 --> 01:20:01,091
<font color=#70DB93>妈的！</font>
Fuck!

794
01:20:02,395 --> 01:20:05,000
<font color=#70DB93>好了 无论如何还是要谢谢你</font>
All right. Thanks for trying, anyway.

795
01:20:05,010 --> 01:20:09,000
<font color=#70DB93>-（你现在打算怎么办？） -我不知道</font>
- 'What are you gonna do now?' - I don't know.

796
01:20:11,000 --> 01:20:12,354
<font color=#70DB93>妈的！</font>
Fuck!

797
01:20:12,487 --> 01:20:16,200
<font color=#70DB93>我们没事 我会再打给你..卡琳？</font>
We're OK. I'll call you once... Karin?

798
01:20:19,701 --> 01:20:23,151
<font color=#70DB93>-现在怎么办？-我们得离开城里 来吧</font>
- Now what? - We've gotta leave town. Come on.

799
01:20:37,258 --> 01:20:39,134
<font color=#70DB93>哇！</font>
Whoa!

800
01:20:40,636 --> 01:20:42,047
<font color=#70DB93>天啊！</font>
Jesus!

801
01:20:44,000 --> 01:20:45,340
<font color=#70DB93>我们走！来！</font>
Let's go! Come on!

802
01:20:52,845 --> 01:20:55,000
<font color=#70DB93>他们正在进行最后的扫荡</font>
They're doing a final sweep.

803
01:20:56,024 --> 01:21:00,020
