945
01:40:11,159 --> 01:40:15,600
<font color=#70DB93>自由不会退缩,自由不会投降!</font>
that freedom will not retreat,freedom will not surrender!

946
01:40:16,589 --> 01:40:20,000
<font color=#70DB93>我们可能被包围了,但是我们并不孤单</font>
We may be besieged,but we are not alone.

947
01:40:20,000 --> 01:40:25,100
<font color=#70DB93>今晚六个欧洲国家的总统和我们站在一起</font>
Standing with us here tonight are six European presidents

948
01:40:25,100 --> 01:40:27,120
<font color=#70DB93>他们跋涉了数千英里</font>
who have travelled thousands of miles

949
01:40:27,132 --> 01:40:29,997
<font color=#70DB93>来和我们一起反抗恐惧和威胁!</font>
in defiance of fear and threats!

950
01:40:31,218 --> 01:40:35,300
<font color=#70DB93>他们六位在这里是因为他们知道独立问题</font>
These six men are here because they know the issue of independence

952
01:40:35,300 --> 01:40:38,289
<font color=#70DB93>今晚将会在这里解决!</font>
is being decided here tonight!

953
01:40:42,018 --> 01:40:48,739
<font color=#70DB93>愿上帝保佑格鲁吉亚人民,格鲁吉亚自由万岁!</font>
May God bless the Georgian people! Long live a free Georgia!

954
01:40:54,863 --> 01:40:58,200
<font color=#70DB93>格鲁吉亚!格鲁吉亚!格鲁吉亚!</font>
Georgia! Georgia! Georgia!

955
01:41:21,000 --> 01:41:23,168
<font color=#70DB93>他们说你会完全康复的</font>
They say you're gonna make a full recovery.

956
01:41:23,303 --> 01:41:27,301
<font color=#70DB93>是吗?6个月!</font>
Yeah? Six months!

957
01:41:27,432 --> 01:41:32,000
<font color=#70DB93>还有..我们的录像?</font>
And... our footage?

958
01:41:32,001 --> 01:41:35,000
<font color=#70DB93>送出去了.正在人权组织那儿</font>
It's out. Human Rights Watch has it.

959
01:41:35,000 --> 01:41:38,354
<font color=#70DB93>反响很大 很多人都开始关注了</font>
It's getting a lot of hits and people are starting to pay attention.

960
01:41:39,901 --> 01:41:42,000
<font color=#70DB93>就像开炮</font>
Not bad for a loose cannon.

961
01:41:42,737 --> 01:41:44,480
<font color=#70DB93>谢谢,兄弟</font>
Thanks, bucko.

962
01:41:45,000 --> 01:41:47,898
<font color=#70DB93>(尽管已经停火并承诺撤军)</font>
'Despite the ceasefire and pledges to withdraw,

963
01:41:48,032 --> 01:41:51,116
<font color=#70DB93>(俄罗斯军队和坦克仍然停留在哥里)</font>
'the Russian troops and tanks remain in Gori,

964
01:41:51,243 --> 01:41:54,000
<font color=#70DB93>(以及格鲁吉亚中部的大片区域)</font>
'and in much of central Georgia.

965
01:41:54,000 --> 01:41:56,000
<font color=#70DB93>(我现在正站在军医院)</font>
'I am standing at the military hospital

966
01:41:56,000 --> 01:41:59,000
<font color=#70DB93>(人们被陆续转移到达这里)</font>
'where displaced people continue to arrive.

967
01:41:59,600 --> 01:42:01,000
<font color=#70DB93>(人们没有其它地方可去)</font>
'People with nowhere else to go,

968
01:42:01,000 --> 01:42:03,331
<font color=#70DB93>(除了暴力,掠夺和杀戮的情景以外什么也没有)</font>
'and nothing but stories of violence, looting and killings.

969
01:42:03,462 --> 01:42:06,000
<font color=#70DB93>战争持续了5天</font>
The war lasted five days.

970
01:42:06,000 --> 01:42:09,000
<font color=#70DB93>(有超过10万人失去了他们的家园)</font>
'More than 100,000 people have lost their homes...

971
01:42:09,000 --> 01:42:11,000
<font color=#70DB93>(数百人被杀害,包括5名记者)</font>
Several hundred people were killed,including five reporters.

972
01:42:11,000 --> 01:42:13,130
<font color=#70DB93>(自战争爆发后的9天以来)</font>
'...since this war began just nine days ago.

973
01:42:13,661 --> 01:42:17,200
<font color=#70DB93>(人们总是问我怎么仍然会发生这样的事)</font>
'People keep asking me how can this still be happening...'

974
01:42:17,200 --> 01:42:20,051
<font color=#70DB93>估计有5万人无家可归</font>
An estimated 50,000 people were made homeless,

975
01:42:20,184 --> 01:42:23,304
<font color=#70DB93>他们的村庄被侵占或遭到了永久性的破坏</font>
their villages permanently destroyed or occupied.

976
01:42:24,437 --> 01:42:29,000
<font color=#70DB93>很多人仍然在难民营居住</font>
Many still live in refugee camps.

977
01:42:30,652 --> 01:42:34,320
<font color=#70DB93>尽管美国和欧洲要求撤军</font>
Despite demands from Europe and the United States to withdraw,

978
01:42:34,445 --> 01:42:38,750
<font color=#70DB93>南奥塞梯和阿布哈兹地区仍然被俄军侵占</font>
the regions of South Ossetia and Abkhazia remain occupied by Russian forces.

980
01:42:39,000 --> 01:42:41,000
<font color=#70DB93>此刻这个国家正在为它的生存而战</font>
This nation is right now fighting for its survival.

981
01:42:41,000 --> 01:42:46,575
<font color=#70DB93>格鲁吉亚继续寻求与西方融为一体</font>
Georgia continues its quest to integrate with the West.

982
01:42:47,000 --> 01:42:50,705
<font color=#70DB93>(这是托马斯.安德斯在格鲁吉亚发回的报道)</font>
'This is Thomas Anders reporting in Georgia.'

983
01:42:55,000 --> 01:43:00,000
<font color=#70DB93>我的丈夫,米哈伊尔.塔波什维利,在艾瑞提村被杀害</font>
My husband, Mikheil Taboshvili.Killed in Eredvi village.

984
01:43:00,010 --> 01:43:02,669
<font color=#70DB93>我的爸爸</font>
My father.

985
01:43:03,000 --> 01:43:07,000
<font color=#70DB93>我的婆婆,纳塔利亚.欧克罗派莱德兹</font>
My mother-in-law, Natalia Okropiridze.

986
01:43:07,010 --> 01:43:10,000
<font color=#70DB93>我的母亲,纳塔利亚.欧克罗派莱德兹</font>
My mother, Natalia Okropiridze.

987
01:43:10,518 --> 01:43:16,104
<font color=#70DB93>在疏散时我父母正在穿过公路</font>
As my parents were being evacuated and they were crossing the road,

988
01:43:17,316 --> 01:43:24,000
<font color=#70DB93>一颗地雷在他们的车前爆炸 弹片直接击中了她的太阳穴 </font>
a mine exploded in front of their car and shrapnel hit her straight in the temple.

989
01:43:24,000 --> 01:43:26,322
<font color=#70DB93>她当场死亡</font>
She died on the spot.

990
01:43:29,159 --> 01:43:31,000
<font color=#70DB93>泽巴辛德兹.塔玛尔,我的母亲</font>
Zambakhidze Tamar, my mother.

991
01:43:31,119 --> 01:43:32,317
<font color=#70DB93>我的妻子</font>
My wife.

992
01:43:32,454 --> 01:43:34,327
<font color=#70DB93>我们的祖母</font>
Our grandmother.

993
01:43:34,913 --> 01:43:39,448
<font color=#70DB93>我的父母被拷问,他们被割开了喉咙</font>
My parents were tortured.Their throats were slit.

994
01:43:42,000 --> 01:43:46,330
<font color=#70DB93>他们被埋在我的后院,这就是我知道的一切</font>
They were buried in our backyard,and that's all we know.

995
01:43:48,175 --> 01:43:51,000
<font color=#70DB93>这是诺达尔.奥提阿什维利,我的父亲</font>
This is Nodar Otiashvili, my father.

996
01:43:52,304 --> 01:43:57,000
<font color=#70DB93>我们以前住在卡维默阿查贝提村</font>
We used to live in Kvemo Achabeti village.

997
01:43:59,000 --> 01:44:02,056
<font color=#70DB93>我是斯科莱特.戈德兹的儿子</font>
I am the son of Socrate Gogidze.

998
01:44:03,000 --> 01:44:08,348
<font color=#70DB93>红十字会的人告诉我</font>
I was told by the Red Cross

999
01:44:08,400 --> 01:44:10,000
<font color=#70DB93>他被埋在我家的花园里</font>
that he was buried in our garden.

1000
01:44:13,504 --> 01:44:15,200
<font color=#70DB93>他是被吊死的</font>
He had been hanged.

1001
01:44:19,000 --> 01:44:23,201
<font color=#70DB93>我是玛丽娜.卡比阿什维利.我过去住在克海维村</font>
I am Marina Kakhbiashvili.I used to live in Kehvi village.

1002
01:44:25,000 --> 01:44:28,000
<font color=#70DB93>在8月8日那天,我们离开了</font>
On August 8th, we left.

1003
01:44:28,019 --> 01:44:31,331
<font color=#70DB93>我的丈夫留在那儿.我的儿子和我丈夫</font>
My husband stayed there.My son and my husband.

1004
01:44:31,461 --> 01:44:36,641
<font color=#70DB93>我儿子那天晚上离开了.我丈夫永远留在了屋子里</font>
My son left that night.My husband stayed in the house.

1005
01:44:47,266 --> 01:44:49,674
<font color=#70DB93>埃卡特琳.帕普利什维利,我的祖母</font>
Ekaterine Papelishvili, my grandmother.

